response = session.get('/echo-route-autobind/' + fragment)
ensure_success(response)
content = response.json()
assert content == echoed
pytest.mark.parametrize('fragment,echoed', [('Hello/World/777', {'one':
    'Hello', 'two': 'World', 'three': '777'}), (
    'Hello%20World!!%20%3F/items/archived', {'one': 'Hello World!! ?',
    'two': 'items', 'three': 'archived'})])
